docs.text:
• Go

    import (
    "context"
    "fmt"
    "log/slog"
    "os"
)

func main() {
    if err := run(context.Background()); err != nil {
        slog.Error("critical failure, closing",
            "error", err)
        os.Exit(1)
    }
}

func run(ctx contex.Context) error {
    // ...
}

  • C Example

    #include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int n, i, sum = 0;

    printf("Enter a positive integer: ");
    scanf("%d", &n);

    for (i = 1; i <= n; ++i) {
        sum += i;
    }

    printf("Sum = %d", sum);
    return 0;
}

  • YAML

    foo:
- bar:
    baz: !!baz
baz: "bar" # something
cux: null # TODO(foo): bar baz
rex: 1.2

    FROM scratch

# copy file
COPY ./foo ./bar

# set env
ENV foo=bar
